Package: bio3dview
Type: Package
Title: Interactive 3D viewing of Bio3D objects 
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Barry", "Grant",
      email = "bjgrant@ucsd.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Functions to link bio3d to the NGLVieweR package and thereby enable
  interactive molecular graphics of single or multi-model PDB objects, ensembles 
  of aligned PDBs (multi-structre PDB sets) and the outputs of PCA, NMA, 
  trajectory analysis etc.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
